CATEGORIES:Personal
DESCRIPTION:\n**URGENT INFORMATION BEFORE YOU ATTEND YOUR APPOINTMENT**\n
  In the last 14 days\, if you have travelled anywhere outside of Canada 
 and are feeling unwell with fever\, and/or cough\, shortness of breath\,
  or have been in close contact with a person who has travelled and is un
 well\, or have been in close contact with a confirmed or probable case o
 f COVID-19\, please consider the following:\n Is your laboratory visit o
 f routine nature that could be delayed for 14 days? If so\, please cance
 l and rebook at a later time.\n If your laboratory visit is of a more ur
 gent nature and cannot be delayed you may attend your scheduled appointm
 ent.\n All patients will be required to use the provided hand sanitizer 
 and don the provided surgical mask when entering our facilities. Please 
 do not bring additional persons with you to the lab unless they are requ
 ired for your support during your appointment.\n\n APPOINTMENT CONFIRMAT
 ION\n\nPatient Service Centre(PSC):  Banff: 305 Lynx Street\nDate:  Satu
 rday\, September 26\, 2020 - 11:40AM\nApproximately 30 minutes\nConfirma
 tion Number:  VK60JNV1\n\nIf you are unable to attend this appointment\,
  please cancel online.\n\nConfirm if you need to fast by reviewing the A
 PL recommended fasting instructions.\n\nOn the day of your Appointment: 
 Arrive only a few minutes early with your requisition\, Provincial Healt
 hcare Card and a piece of government issued identification. Due to physi
 cal distancing requirements we do not have space in our waiting rooms fo
 r early arrivals and are unlikely to be able to serve you prior to your 
 appointment time.\n\n\nThe information in this email and any attachments
  is confidential and for the sole use of the intended recipient(s). If y
 ou have received this email in error\, notify us by forwarding this emai
 l to palfeedback@cls.ab.ca stating you are not the correct recipient\; a
 nd then delete all copies immediately including your trash/deleted folde
 r.\n\n
DTEND:20200926T175000Z
DTSTAMP:20230922T040320Z
DTSTART:20200926T174000Z
