DESCRIPTION:Hi Mardi\,\n\n\n\nThe interview will last roughly 30 minutes 
 and will be held at our main building: 10921 14 Street NE\, Calgary\, AB
  ( https://www.google.ca/maps/place/Novatel+Inc./@51.1500733\,-114.03294
 28\,17z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x5371644a0a499135:0x2ff07faea04c7bfc!8m2!3d51.1
 500733!4d-114.0307541). When you enter the parking lot\, it is the large
 r and flatter of the two Hexagon buildings.\n\n\n\nTransportation:\n\nIf
  you plan on driving\, you can park in our visitor parking lot.\n\nIf yo
 u plan on using public transportation\, let me know and I can attach dir
 ections for you to our building.\n\n\n\nUpon Arrival:\n\nOnce you arrive
  you will meet our receptionist\, Julie\, with whom you can request for 
 Jason if he is not already at reception waiting for you.\n\nPlease arriv
 e at 2:55pm as you will have to sign in and verify your identity with Ju
 lie as well. Please ensure you have a piece of government issued ID on y
 ou as it is required to enter our Controlled Goods facility.\n\nAddition
 ally\, if you plan on driving\, you will have to register your license p
 late with Julie.\n\nIn the event that someone is not there\, you can cal
 l me at 403-295-4481\, and I will let you in and retrieve Jason and Juli
 e.\n\n\n\nCOVID-19 Protocol:\n\nAs of June 1st\, 2022\, we have made our
  mask mandate optional. If you are immunocompromised or would prefer if 
 everyone involved in the interview to wear a mask\, let me know and I ca
 n accommodate you. If you do not have a mask we can provide one for you.
 \n\nIf you are feeling unwell on the day of the interview\, please let m
 e know and we can discuss either moving online to using Microsoft Teams 
 or changing the date of your interview.\n\n\n\nPlease let me know if you
  have any questions in the meantime.\n\n\n\nKind regards\,\n\nSarah Gilh
 olme\nTalent Acquisition Associate\nAutonomy & Positioning division\nHex
 agon\nT: +1 403.295.4481\nE: sarah.gilholme@hexagon.com<mailto:sarah.gil
 holme@hexagon.com>\nOffice: Hexagon Calgary Campus\n10921 14 Street NE\n
