BEGIN:VEVENT
CREATED:20190725T030920Z
DESCRIPTION:Hey CBS Alumni!\n\nWe’d like to invite you to a reunion\, Mon
 day August 12 from 5-7 PM. \n\nOn the Beach (Weather Permitting)\, behin
 d 159 Masters Cove SE\, Calgary\, AB T3M 2N8 (Where class was held)\n\nS
 uper casual\, come early\, leave late\, (or vice versa) whatever works b
 est for you and your fam! \n\nBring a snack to share\, and bring yoursel
 f a picnic dinner if you choose. \n\nHoping to see you all there and see
  how grown up these babes all are!\n\nPlease RSVP. Thanks!\n\nCamilla Pr
 ice ICCE\, LCCE\, CD(DONA)\nCalgary Birth Services\nwww.calgarybirthserv
 ices.com
DTEND;TZID=GMT-0400:20190812T190000
DTSTAMP:20230922T040626Z
